   Tuesday's Markets:
   Dollar Sinks
   Still Lower
   Versus Mark
   ---
   Bond Rally Is Stalled;
   Blue-Chip Stocks
   See Mild Retreat
   ----
   By Tom Herman and Michael R. Sesit
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
